{"tid":1419524,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【請大家】【不要破壞紅綠燈】。【不要破壞紅綠燈】","createTime":"2019-08-06T01:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:50:42.000Z","uid":230544,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"52c5aded850c7ffdf36fc1029bd5ad17d2515baa","tid":1419524,"uid":230544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:42:24.000Z","msg":"今朝出去睇到<br />\n好多紅綠燈都唔著<br />\n好多司機以為自己係車神<br />\n見無燈就係咁呠行人<br />\n<br />\n老人家又過唔到馬路 係到係咁等<br />\n一直無車讓佢<br />\n<br />\n我好驚佢地有咩意外<br />\n<br />\n有渣開車都知 有好多司機渣車係唔用腦<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家，不要破壞紅綠燈<br />\n破壞紅綠燈出意外<br />\n影響既只有平民<br />\n<br />\n請大家幫幫忙，因為真係好危險"},{"pid":"d96927a8ee4dc6e7691633a7a1c4752c6ab7935c","tid":1419524,"uid":230544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:42:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b7b82f5c984847646f53061e525ad0c9ea380a39","tid":1419524,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:43:09.000Z","msg":"政府熄架啦"},{"pid":"939227dd8664e967290fdbc5040cf76cf9385043","tid":1419524,"uid":230544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7b82f5c984847646f53061e525ad0c9ea380a39","tid":1419524,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:43:09.000Z","msg":"政府熄架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:46:37.000Z","msg":"咁提下身邊同屋企既老人家小心<br />\n<br />\n見到就幫手報1823"},{"pid":"547c7b8097f66cb17d13ce6450d775453e925150","tid":1419524,"uid":230544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:50:42.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}